snippet.title: A.G.E gameplay (PC Game, 1991)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for A.G.E (aka a.g.e. - advanced galactic empire), Dos PC game produced by Coktel Vision in 1991 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/age/5620/
Watching the intro and exploring the interface in this science fiction adventure.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
